data.description: SECULUDED DIAMOND IN THE DESERT ~  Just Reduced -- This Morongo Valley 5 ( FIVE ) Acre HORSE PROPERTY is NOT LAND LOCKED and this Parcel is connected to over 220 Acres of Bureau of Land Management Mountain Property that WILL NEVER  be built on.  Enjoy taking your horses up and over the Mountains while enjoying unobstructed panoramic views of majestic Mount Jacinto and of the beautiful San Bernardino Hills.  This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath,  1947 Sq Ft Secluded  Home  is located between two desert washes ( Water ) and has a Private Bridge that can be secured for total privacy if desired.  This 1947 Sq Ft of living space boasts a Master Bedroom and Bath upstairs with a large open balcony / den / office which overlooks the family room.  The Family Room offers plenty of light through 15 Foot Tall windows that provide a spectacular view and has a free standing wood burning stove for  cool nights.  There are 2 Bedrooms, 1 Bath downstairs along with a laundry room and separate family room with its own fireplace.  Outside you will find an in ground Large Jacuzzi and a work / storage shed.  There are two patios with One in Front (  BY ENTRANCE ) and the  Second covered one in the back ( WHICH HAS SPECTACULAR VEIWS ).  There is plenty of room for two or  more horse corrals putting one in the back and just off the parking area in the front of the home.  THIS SECLUDED DIAMOND IN THE DESERT is ONE OF A KIND opportunity to purchase a Private  HORSE PROPERTY JEM with its OWN WELL at a Great price!  Its a fantastic location and its even close to Palm Springs, International Airport and Joshua Tree National Monument.
